data.description: Escape the hustle and bustle of city life and find your family retreat in this idyllic countryside haven. This property offers the ultimate escape from city life. Explore the nearby trails for mountain biking and hiking, allowing your family to connect with nature and enjoy the serene surroundings. Privacy is paramount here, ensuring that you can unwind and recharge away in the backyard pool and cabana.  This well-maintained home comes with recent upgrades, including a new roof and HVAC system, so you can move in worry-free. Every handyman will feel at home in two wired workshops. Plus, it's a paradise for animal enthusiasts, with open arms for your horses, chickens, and other creatures. This property stretches ten acres with four thoughtfully fenced acres. Your animals can roam freely and graze in a secure and picturesque setting. Experience the tranquility and freedom of country living with all the amenities of the Triangle.
